<p><img src="/media/2014/12/bitpoint.jpg" alt="Bitpoint Group Picture" /></p>

<p>Great turnout at the last Hong Kong Bitcoin meetup of 2014. Stacy Herbert and Max Keiser, who were in town filming episodes of their RT show <a href="http://rt.com/shows/keiser-report/">Keiser Report</a> also dropped by and shared their great knowledge of Bitcoin, Media and World Finance with us.
See you all again in 2015! Stay update about our meetings through our <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Bitcoin-HK/">Meetup group</a>.</p>
